4. Set path to command line utilities {#MSYS_PATH}
==================================================

The command line utilities are located in:

    c:\MinGW\msys\1.0\bin

Start > Control Panel > System > Advanced System Settings > Environment Variables > Path

![](mingw_path.png)

@tip_s
For the sake of this guide, the simplest solution has been shown.
@tip_e

5. Utilities included with UnixShellUtils {#MSYS_UNIX_SHELL_UTILS}
==================================================================

As stated previously, the command line utilities are located in:

    c:\MinGW\msys\1.0\bin

These are the files included with [UnixShellUtils] [unix_shell_utils]:

    c:\UnixShellUtils\usr\bin\cat.exe   
    c:\UnixShellUtils\usr\bin\cmp.exe   
    c:\UnixShellUtils\usr\bin\cp.exe    
